#: dist/converse-no-dependencies.js:51644
msgid "Sorry, could not decrypt a received OMEMO message due to an error."
msgstr "No s'ha pogut desxifrar un missatge OMEMO rebut a causa d'un error."

#: dist/converse-no-dependencies.js:51670
